import React from 'react';
import { Timeline, Text } from '@mantine/core';

function TimelineComponent() {
    return (
        <Timeline active={1} bulletSize={24} lineWidth={2}>
          <Timeline.Item color="lime" title="Mathematical Olympiad Lecturer">
          <Text color="dimmed" size="sm">Lectured Mathematical Olimpiad Seminaries in <Text variant="link" component="span" inherit href="https://fi.ort.edu.uy/78235/33">Universidad ORT</Text> and Universidad de Montevideo.</Text>
            <Text color="dimmed" size="sm">Also weekly workshops in PREU High School.</Text>
            <Text size="xs" mt={4}>2019 - 2020</Text>
          </Timeline.Item>

          <Timeline.Item title="Adjunct Proffesor">
            <Text color="dimmed" size="sm">Adjunct proffesor in the course of Discrete Mathematics in Universidad ORT Uruguay.</Text>
            <Text size="xs" mt={4}>2020</Text>
          </Timeline.Item>
    
          <Timeline.Item title="Software Engineer">
            <Text color="dimmed" size="sm">Started as a Junior Software Engineer Intern and then worked as a Software Engineer I in TangoCode Inc.</Text>
            <Text color="dimmed" size="sm">I worked in agile software projects and web development related to Digital Marketing in the product Chassis.</Text>
            <Text size="xs" mt={4}>2020 - 2022</Text>
          </Timeline.Item>

          <Timeline.Item title="Problem Selection Committee">
            <Text color="dimmed" size="sm">Volunteering in problem formulation and selection, and jury for the Uruguayan National Mathematical Olympiads.</Text>
            <Text color="dimmed" size="sm">Also participated as jury in the international Olimpíada Matemática Rioplatense alongside world-class Professors in Mathematics.</Text>
            <Text size="xs" mt={4}>2019 - ongoing</Text>
          </Timeline.Item>
        </Timeline>

      );
}

export default TimelineComponent;
